title: (Thurs Early Bird) Amy and Lunchbox Battles on Getting on TV +  Morgan Reviews: Bill & Ted’s Excellent Adventure + Elder vs. Millennial: Can Eddie Win It All?
itunes:title: (Thurs Early Bird) Amy and Lunchbox Battles on Getting on TV +  Morgan Reviews: Bill & Ted’s Excellent Adventure + Elder vs. Millennial: Can Eddie Win It All?
description:
Amy and Lunchbox are now in a heated battle to both be featured on Amy’ sister’s HGTV’s Building Roots. Who will make it on an episode?? We made Morgan give her millennial review of an 80’s movie that Bobby and Eddie both loved but she had never seen! And Eddie and Morgan face off this week in Elder vs. Millennial with the title on the line.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
